               <msContents>
                  <summary>I)Introduction (fols. 1ra-11vb)&#xD;
- Mäqdǝmä wängel “Introduction to the Gospels” (fols. 1ra-6vb) &#xD;
- Letter of Eusebius to Carpianus (fols. 6vb-7rb)&#xD;
- Canon tables (fols. 7va-11ra)&#xD;
- On the reliability of the Gospels (fol. 11va-vb)&#xD;
II) Gospel of Matthew (fols. 1va-64vb)&#xD;
- Biography of Matthew (fol. 11va-vb)&#xD;
- Bǝsratä Matewos “Gospel of Matthew” (fols. 14ra-64vb)&#xD;
- Postscript (fol. 64vb)&#xD;
III) Gospel of Mark (fols. 64va-99ra)&#xD;
- Biography of Mark (fols. 64va-65ra)&#xD;
- List of the “tituli” for the Gospel of Mark: 48 titles (fol. 65ra-vb)&#xD;
- Bǝsratä Marqos “Gospel of Mark” (fols. 68ra-98vb)&#xD;
- Postscript (fol. 99ra)&#xD;
IV) Gospel of Luke (fols. 99ra-157ra)&#xD;
- Biography of Luke (fol. 99rb-va), preceded by a prayer (fol. 99ra-rb)&#xD;
- List of the “tituli” for the Gospel of Luke: 83 titles (fols. 99va-100vb) &#xD;
- Bǝsratä Luqas “Gospel of Luke” (fols. 103ra-157ra)&#xD;
- Postscript (fol. 157ra)&#xD;
V) Gospel of John (fols. 157ra-201ra)&#xD;
- Biography of John (fols. 157ra-158ra)&#xD;
- List of the “tituli” for the Gospel of John: 20 titles (fol. 158ra-rb)&#xD;
- Bǝsratä Yoḥannǝs “Gospel of John” (fols. 160ra-200vb)&#xD;
- Postscript (fol. 201ra)&#xD;
&#xD;
Additio 1.</summary>
