                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>In Text I, Mäqdǝmä wängel is incomplete, the final part of the seventh and the entire eighth "periods of instruction" missing. For details s. R.W. COWLEY, “New Testament Introduction in the Andemta Commentary Tradition”, Ostkirchliche Studien 26, 1977, 144-92; here esp. 160-2; R. ZUURMOND, Novum Testamentum Aethiopice: the Synoptic Gospels, Part I: General Introduction, Part II: Edition of the Gospel of Mark, Stuttgart, 1989 (AeF 27), 6-36.</note>
                     <note>The "Biography of Matthew" is merged with the part "On the reliability of the Gospels".</note>
                     <note>Additional leaves with miniatures were infixed in the recent time, to "illuminate" the Ms.</note>
                     <note>Decorated quire marks.</note>
                     <note/>
                     <note>The Golden Gospel of ʾAmbäsät Kidāna Mǝḥrat church.</note>
                  </msItem>
